measure.CatchLine: Removes requirements related to wildfire hazards for purposes of developing an accessory dwelling unit on lands zoned for rural residential uses or a replacement dwelling on lands zoned for resource uses.
measure.MeasureSummary: Digest: This Act strikes fire hazards requirements for rural second homes. (Flesch Readability Score: 61.3). [Digest: The Act updates wildfire hazard language for rural homes. (Flesch Readability Score: 66.1).] [Defines "high wildfire hazard area"] Removes requirements related to wildfire hazards for purposes of developing an accessory dwelling unit on lands zoned for rural residential uses or a replacement dwelling on lands zoned for resource uses.
measure.RelatingToFull: Relating to wildfire hazard requirements for nonurban dwellings.
measure.RelatingTo: Relating to wildfire hazard requirements for nonurban dwellings.
measure.AtTheRequestOf: (at the request of Senate Interim Committee on Natural Resources and Wildfire)
